                    improve reading and basic understanding. Tutorials, references, and examples are constantly 
                    reviewed to avoid errors, but we cannot warrant full correctness of all content. While using this site, 
                    you agree to have read and accepted our terms of use, cookie and privacy policy. <br />
                    &copy; 1999-2016 by Refsnes Data. All Rights Reserved.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
            
        </footer>

    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>

